@startuml
actor Teacher
participant WebApp
participant "Core API" as API
participant AttendanceService
participant Database
Teacher -> WebApp: Mark student attendance
WebApp -> API: POST /api/v1/student-attendance
API -> AttendanceService: validate and record
AttendanceService -> Database: insert attendance and audit log
Database --> AttendanceService: record
AttendanceService --> API: result
API --> WebApp: 201 Created
@enduml
